  "text": "LDH release assay. Cytotoxicity was measured by cell lactate dehydrogenase (LDH) release as previously described [CITATION_1] . Briefly, culture supernatants were harvested in a 96-well flat-bottom assay plate. A substrate mixture consisting of 0.05 M L-(ϩ)-lactic acid, 7 ϫ 10 Ϫ4 M p-iodonitrotetrazolium violet, and 3 ϫ 10",
